Text: So... i don't mean to be rude what-so ever but i was wondering if you missed the last episode on purpose or what?  I know its hard to get these out so quickly while subtitling them.  But, i would greatly appreciate that episode.  I look forward every week like many do i am sure for the new episode.  Right now there is just some new weird person's 342 episode.  Hope to see it soon and even if not thank you for your hard work.
